videos.description: Harrison Hornery gets the rock then turns and fires for a beautiful fallaway jumper with seconds left on the shot clock.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Harrison Hornery sinks a beautiful fallaway jumper) 2022/02/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harrison Hornery sinks a beautiful fallaway jumper

videos.description: Reese Dixon-Waters dishes a textbook dime to Max Agbonkpolo who back cuts to the basket for a reverse layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dixon-Waters dishes a slick backdoor pass to Agbonkpolo) 2022/02/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dixon-Waters dishes a slick backdoor pass to Agbonkpolo

videos.description: Max Agbonkpolo anticipates the steal then goes coast to coast with Ethan Anderson who goes up for a nice layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Agbonkpolo fuels up for a steal then connects with Anderson for a layup) 2022/02/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Agbonkpolo fuels up for a steal then connects with Anderson for a layup

videos.description: Drew Peterson sinks his 17th point of the game with this nice fadeaway jump shot.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Drew Peterson pivots and nails the jump shot) 2022/02/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Drew Peterson pivots and nails the jump shot

videos.description: Jaime Jaquez Jr. drives through defenders and goes up for the strong and-1 bucket.

videos.headline: Jaime Jaquez Jr. drives strong for the hoop and the harm

videos.description: UCLA's David Singleton steals the rock and pushes up the court to Jaylen Clark who shows off nice footwork for the and-1 bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (UCLA's steal leads to Jaylen Clark’s impressive and-1) 2022/02/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCLA's steal leads to Jaylen Clark's impressive and-1

videos.description: Tyger Campbell steps through defenders in the paint and tosses the rock up for an and-1 bucket.

videos.headline: Tyger Campbell somehow gets this and-1 to fall

videos.description: Drew Peterson crosses in front of defenders and absolutely drains his forth 3-pointer of the night.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (USC's Drew Peterson steps back and sinks a crucial 3) 2022/02/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: USC's Drew Peterson steps back and sinks a crucial 3

videos.description: Reese Dixon-Waters steals the ball from UCLA in the final seconds of the game, then connects with Max Agbonkpolo who lays it up to secure the win for USC.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Reese Dixon-Waters' steal seals USC's victory vs. UCLA) 2022/02/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Reese Dixon-Waters' steal seals USC's victory vs. UCLA
